Package games.negative.framework.command.annotation

Annotation Interface CommandInfo

@Target(TYPE) @Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface CommandInfo
CommandInfo

The ability to initialize your command without multiple annotations or using the super methods

    • shortCommands

      String[] shortCommands
      The shortcommand alias of the command

      This is intended to be a shortcut for the command For example if you have a command called "gamemode creative" and you want to use "gmc" as a shortcut You can do this by having a short command called "gmc"

      Returns:
